- {{% resource_link "fa89956a-eed6-42dc-bb2e-155ed8cab4c2" "fMRI Bootcamp Part 3 - Univariate analysis" %}}
- {{% resource_link "bf4709f4-2964-4596-bc81-910942f4ce48" "fMRI Bootcamp Part 4 - Multivariate analysis" %}}
- {{% resource_link "93adf182-a664-4055-bcea-daa96eabd253" "fMRI Bootcamp Part 5 - Multivoxel pattern analysis (MVPA)" %}}
- {{% resource_link "97adf51e-c636-4366-bf30-579c56ee6a5d" "fMRI Bootcamp Part 6 - Classification" %}} 
- {{% resource_link "6498eb9c-ad2a-4c4b-a808-606d30b174e6" "fMRI Bootcamp Part 7 - Representational similarity" %}}
